# Goals
## Technical goals
Be able to do all of the following file system and programming tasks.
* Read files asychronously.
* Process JSON, XML, SQL, and streams.
* Read and write Kafka
* Read and write elastic
* Pop up a node cluster
* Set up an API sample
* Connect to most common databases
  * SQL - Postgres
  * Document - Mongo OR Dynamo
  * Graph : neo4j
  * Search Document : Elastic
  * Key value : redis, memcached
## Style Goals
Be able to clearly write the following:
  * Point-free functional interfaces
  * First class object factories
  * 